00:00:32.272 --> 00:00:35.821
SEPTEMBER ONE NINETEEN NINETY SEVEN.

00:00:35.821 --> 00:00:41.298
SURVIVOR, MRS. REGINA PREIZLER, BORN HUBER.

00:00:41.298 --> 00:00:45.474
INTERVIEWER, YESHAYAHU PERY. CITY, RECHOVOT.

00:00:45.474 --> 00:00:48.298
COUNTRY, ISRAEL. LANGUAGE, YIDDISH.

00:00:49.974 --> 00:00:54.103
TODAY, SEPTEMBER ONE, NINETEEN NINETY SEVEN,

00:00:54.345 --> 00:00:56.634
HERE IN RECHOVOT, ISRAEL,

00:00:56.910 --> 00:01:05.190
MYSELF, YESHAYAHU PERY AS AN INTERVIEWER IN THE NAME OF SURVIVORS OF THE SHOAH VISUAL HISTORY FOUNDATION,

00:01:05.415 --> 00:01:09.985
I DO HAVE THE HONOR TO START THE INTERVIEW WITH THE SURVIVOR

00:01:10.005 --> 00:01:12.801
MRS. REGINA PREIZLER,

00:01:13.262 --> 00:01:15.602
EH, LANGUAGE, YIDDISH.

00:01:18.206 --> 00:01:21.018
SHALOM froy Regina Preyzler.

00:01:21.682 --> 00:01:25.254
mit ayer erloybenish fangen mir on yetst mitn INTERVIEW.

00:01:25.445 --> 00:01:30.536
ikh volt aykh gevolt fregn etlekhe kurtse fragn, un shpeter vet ir onheybn tsu dertseyln.

00:01:30.828 --> 00:01:36.155
iz koydem-kol, zayt azoy gut, shtelt zikh for far der CAMERA un zogt vi ir heyst.

00:01:37.063 --> 00:01:44.660
ikh bin GEVERET Preyzler, Regina, fun RECHOVOT.

00:01:45.088 --> 00:01:47.496
vu zent ir geboyrn gevorn?

00:01:47.597 --> 00:01:50.280
in Siget, Rumenye.

00:01:50.724 --> 00:01:53.542
velkhn yor, velkhe date zent ir geboyrn gevorn?

00:01:53.289 --> 00:01:55.945
in fertsnter yor, in fertsntn.

00:01:57.795 --> 00:01:59.882
in fertsntn, velkhe monat?

00:01:59.916 --> 00:02:01.859
in april.

00:02:00.815 --> 00:02:01.737
april.

00:02:04.140 --> 00:02:07.796
heyst dos, vi alt zent ir, biz hundert un tsvontsik?

00:02:07.570 --> 00:02:11.733
ikh meyn az se makht oys dray un akhtsik shoyn? ikh veys nisht.

00:02:11.058 --> 00:02:12.824
biz hundert un tsvontsik.

00:02:13.235 --> 00:02:17.212
zayt azoy gut zogt mir, vi hot geheysn ayer tate olevasholem?

00:02:17.166 --> 00:02:25.343
Avrom. er iz geboyrn in eyn, in eyn toyznt akht hundert akhtsik.

00:02:26.718 --> 00:02:28.569
vi iz geven zayn familye?

00:02:28.735 --> 00:02:31.999
Avram, Hober.

00:02:30.701 --> 00:02:32.062
Hober.

00:02:33.131 --> 00:02:35.015
vi iz er geboyrn gevorn?

00:02:35.716 --> 00:02:39.127
vel mir zogn in Siget, in Rumenye. in Rumenyen.

00:02:39.543 --> 00:02:42.541
un vi hot geheysn ayer muter, olevasholem?

00:02:42.606 --> 00:02:44.807
Ester.

00:02:44.923 --> 00:02:49.561
zi iz geboyrn in eyn toyznt akht hundert zeks un akhtsik.

00:02:50.057 --> 00:02:52.701
un vu iz zi geboyrn gevorn?

00:02:51.757 --> 00:02:53.915
oykhet nor d-,

00:02:54.073 --> 00:02:57.172
vi iz geven ir familye fun der heym, gedenkt ir?

00:02:57.076 --> 00:02:58.033
Toyb.

00:02:57.903 --> 00:02:58.707
Toyb.

00:03:01.323 --> 00:03:02.670
Toyb.

00:03:02.865 --> 00:03:08.074
ir hot gehat brider, shvester? zayt azoy gut, git mir di nemen.

00:03:08.148 --> 00:03:13.416
der groyser bruder iz geboyrn in eyn toyznt nayn hundert fir.

00:03:14.795 --> 00:03:16.241
vi hot er geheysn?

00:03:15.978 --> 00:03:21.359
Leyzer Lazar ikh veys... un

00:03:18.812 --> 00:03:19.667
yo.

00:03:21.578 --> 00:03:23.466
er iz avek keyn Oyshvits.

00:03:23.334 --> 00:03:25.016
dos veln mir nokh redn shpeter.

00:03:25.393 --> 00:03:27.716
yetst, der tsveyter bruder?

00:03:27.740 --> 00:03:29.484
di shvester koydem,

00:03:29.038 --> 00:03:30.635
koydem di shvester.

00:03:30.119 --> 00:03:38.007
di shvester iz geboyrn in in tsen. eyn toyznt nayn hundert tsen.

00:03:38.814 --> 00:03:41.691
oykhet in Rumenyen. Hober.

00:03:42.858 --> 00:03:44.371
un geheysn hot zi?

00:03:44.660 --> 00:03:46.141
Honi.

00:03:45.221 --> 00:03:46.093
Khani.

00:03:46.824 --> 00:03:49.791
un er bru- nokh a bruder hot ir gehat?

00:03:46.861 --> 00:03:51.175
yo, yo, Yozhef.

00:03:49.794 --> 00:03:50.548
ve-

00:03:51.556 --> 00:03:53.622
yener iz geboyrn in tsvelef.

00:03:54.637 --> 00:03:56.167
oykhet in der zelb-...

00:03:55.241 --> 00:03:57.134
oykh oykh in Siget.

00:03:57.867 --> 00:04:00.051
er hot geven a gold arbayter.

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:05.668
zayt azoy gut, froy Regina,

00:04:05.825 --> 00:04:06.582
un

00:04:06.582 --> 00:04:09.330
bamit zikh a bisl tsu dermanen

00:04:10.112 --> 00:04:11.931
di kinder-yorn, fun der heym.

00:04:11.931 --> 00:04:16.872
s'iz lange yorn tsurik, ober UNK zikh tsu derman. vos gedenkt ir? vi hot zikh gelebt?

00:04:16.822 --> 00:04:19.516
 s'iz geven zeyer shver.

00:04:19.910 --> 00:04:22.707
ober vos? ikh bin gegan tsu der arbet.

00:04:23.157 --> 00:04:28.531
un ikh hob gearbet, me hot mir zeyer lib gehat vayl ikh bin zeyer ernst un farlozt.

00:04:29.163 --> 00:04:30.777
bay vos hot ir gearbet?

00:04:29.735 --> 00:04:31.301
bay kaplekh.

00:04:31.778 --> 00:04:34.609
un me fleg mikh shikn tsu der post

00:04:34.947 --> 00:04:38.062
mit peklekh tsu shikn in farshidene pletser.

00:04:38.149 --> 00:04:39.949
un s'iz geven a vayml

00:04:40.021 --> 00:04:44.211
vos me hot durkhgekukt, un ikh hob mitgenumen farshidene aktn.

00:04:44.290 --> 00:04:48.776
un ikh hob zey gegebn tsu farshteyn. un ikh hob gegebn a bakshish oykh.

00:04:49.779 --> 00:04:56.953
me hot mir azoy ongezogt, "du," ikh "zog nisht ver du bist, vos, nor koydem di peklekh zoln durkhgeyn."

00:04:57.254 --> 00:04:59.087
un ikh bin tsurikgekumen,

00:04:59.161 --> 00:05:03.426
ikh hob gebroykht batsoln vifl se hot gekost, un m'iz geven shtark tsufridn,

00:05:03.518 --> 00:05:05.683
"Regina bist a mentsh."

00:05:06.980 --> 00:05:11.007
Regina, zayt azoy gut, dertseylt nor a bisl fun frierike yorn.

00:05:11.216 --> 00:05:15.412
fun der heym, az ir gedenkt als meydele, ir hot zikh gelernt ergets? dertseylt mir a bisl.

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:18.653
nu, nu, ikh bin gegan in shul, vifl ikh hob mir gekent dermanen, ikh bin,

00:05:18.703 --> 00:05:21.786
keyn gute zakhn iz nisht gevezn, m-...

00:05:20.987 --> 00:05:22.538
in velkhe shul zent ir gegangen?

00:05:22.450 --> 00:05:24.242
in di rumeynishe shul.

00:05:24.024 --> 00:05:26.212
vifl klasn hot ir geendikt?

00:05:25.228 --> 00:05:27.359
fir. nor fir.

00:05:27.633 --> 00:05:29.264
un nokh dem hob ikh mikh

00:05:29.661 --> 00:05:32.012
genumen, ikh hob mikh gevolt lernen neyen.

00:05:32.554 --> 00:05:36.627
ober ikh hob nisht gekent, der rukn hot mikh vey geton. ikh hob nisht getoygt.

00:05:36.627 --> 00:05:40.670
bin ikh arayngegangen in der fabrik dort, un ikh hob geven

00:05:40.670 --> 00:05:42.137
shtark farlozt.

00:05:42.236 --> 00:05:43.973
far alemen un,

00:05:44.090 --> 00:05:45.883
ikh hob gearbet biz

00:05:45.954 --> 00:05:49.804
di ungern zenen arayngekumen, un biz me hot tsugeshpart.

00:05:51.176 --> 00:05:52.726
zayt azoy gut,

00:05:52.726 --> 00:05:58.410
dertseylt mir a bisl vegn ayer bruder, ayere shvester. vi, vi hot zikh gelebt in der heym?

00:05:58.186 --> 00:05:59.327
shver.

00:05:59.695 --> 00:06:02.556
der bruder hot ongehoybn arbetn.

00:06:03.725 --> 00:06:05.301
er iz geven a shuster.

00:06:05.601 --> 00:06:09.892
un er hot gearbet un er hot fardint un ales, nor in shtub.

00:06:10.550 --> 00:06:12.085
di shvester nisht.

00:06:12.183 --> 00:06:16.010
der anderer bruder, yener hot shoyn fardint zeyer sheyn.

00:06:17.174 --> 00:06:22.808
er iz avek keyn Budapest un er hot fardint un er hot undz oysgehaltn ale.

00:06:22.905 --> 00:06:27.584
un er hot gezogt, "mame, zog mir velkhe shtub vilstu koyfn in Siget.

00:06:27.956 --> 00:06:31.820
ikh hob gelt." er hot fardint. nu,

00:06:31.909 --> 00:06:35.276
zenen di ungern, ales geven arayngeneyt in di hoyzn,

00:06:35.380 --> 00:06:39.331
un un di reklekh do bay di kregn, bay di leng,

00:06:39.386 --> 00:06:42.312
me hot avekgetrogn, men iz ongekumen keyn Daytshland,

00:06:42.390 --> 00:06:44.819
ales avekgevorfn, me hot gornisht.

00:06:45.834 --> 00:06:53.507
zayt azoy gut, dertseylt mir a bisl, vos gedenk ir vegn ayer mamen, in der heym? vi hot zikh ayer mame aherge- der ta- vos iz geshen mitn tatn?

00:06:53.053 --> 00:06:55.895
er iz avek, ikh hob, im ikh hob nisht gekent.

00:06:55.723 --> 00:06:58.114
vos, vos veyst ir, vos hot men aykh dertseylt?

00:06:58.467 --> 00:07:00.885
me hot nisht geredt, az ikh bin geven a kind.

00:07:01.028 --> 00:07:05.079
ikh bin geven, az az er iz avek, er iz dokh geblibn der fertsnter krig.

00:07:05.172 --> 00:07:08.095
nu, mit vifl ikh hob gekent zayn,

00:07:08.280 --> 00:07:09.672
koydem dos,

00:07:09.833 --> 00:07:11.347
ikh veys nisht.

00:07:10.910 --> 00:07:13.267
iz er gefaln in tsayt fun di milkhome?

00:07:12.997 --> 00:07:16.688
zikher iz er in der milkhome. keyn mol iz er nisht aheymgekumen.

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:19.156
iz di mame geven an almone.

00:07:18.656 --> 00:07:19.603
an almone.

00:07:19.702 --> 00:07:22.295
vos UNK, vi hot zikh an eytse gegebn di mame?

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:25.274
men hot ir gegebn a shtikl shtitse, nisht keyn sakh.

00:07:25.874 --> 00:07:30.173
un di kinder, vifl, ver vi azoy se hot fardint hot gegebn, men iz gelebt,

00:07:30.853 --> 00:07:34.624
s'iz nisht geven tsu gring, ober azoy hot zikh es gefirt.

00:07:37.472 --> 00:07:41.888
ir kent mir a bisl dertseyln, vi hot oysgezen ayer shtub? vu hot ir gevoynt?

00:07:41.932 --> 00:07:45.999
oy, zeyer balebatish.

00:07:45.999 --> 00:07:47.526
nisht keyn groyse shtub,

00:07:47.779 --> 00:07:50.306
nor zeyer balebatish, un yidish.

00:07:50.752 --> 00:07:52.742
mayn mame iz geven opgeshoyrn.

00:07:52.818 --> 00:07:55.651
di brider zenen gegan davenen.

00:07:55.651 --> 00:07:58.965
un zey hobn zikh gefirt azoy vi me broykh.

00:07:58.965 --> 00:08:00.630
balebat-, un in shtub oykhet.

00:08:00.699 --> 00:08:07.240
fun vifl, zeyer pinktlekh hot zi gekokht un gegebn, un me ho'mir nisht gefilt tsu shtark

00:08:07.240 --> 00:08:11.722
groyse tsores. s'iz geven argere fun undz.

00:08:11.742 --> 00:08:15.685
un ZE HU, me hot undz avekgefirt...

00:08:15.930 --> 00:08:17.325
zayt azoy gut,

00:08:17.533 --> 00:08:21.645
kent ir zikh dermanen, vi flegt di mame tsugreytn a shabes in der heym?

00:08:24.850 --> 00:08:27.335
oy, hot zi gemakht gute falshe fish.

00:08:27.440 --> 00:08:29.183
zey lign mir in tam.

00:08:29.340 --> 00:08:33.547
vayl in der fabrik bay der mashin fraytik tsu nakhts ven ikh hob gearbet

00:08:33.626 --> 00:08:35.905
hob ikh gezen di mame mitn

00:08:35.995 --> 00:08:40.930
shvartsn kleyd, mitn vaysn shirtsele ongeton,

00:08:41.116 --> 00:08:47.199
un un vi azoy zi firt zikh, herstu, git zi di di falshe fish, itst es ikh zey.

00:08:47.359 --> 00:08:52.492
ikh hob geveynt un ikh hob geredt tsu mir bay der mashin in der fabrik.

00:08:52.638 --> 00:08:59.425
zeyer balebatish. zi hot gekont zeyer gut kokhn. fun a bisl hot zi gemakht a sakh. zi iz geven a baleboste a groyse.

00:09:03.922 --> 00:09:07.463
ir hot dermant az, vegn religyezn lebn.

00:09:07.007 --> 00:09:07.674
yo.

00:09:07.463 --> 00:09:10.171
vos v-, s'iz geven bay aykh in shtot

00:09:10.171 --> 00:09:12.742
shuln, me fleg davenen?

00:09:10.934 --> 00:09:14.991
a s-, a sakh. a sakh rabonim.

00:09:15.178 --> 00:09:19.213
s'iz geven a sakh rabonim, un shuln. yeshives.

00:09:19.394 --> 00:09:22.965
Siget iz geven groys, un...

00:09:23.683 --> 00:09:28.926
ir hot gehat epes a zeydn, UNCLE, epes kroyvim, akhuts di noente mishpokhe?

00:09:26.978 --> 00:09:33.898
ikh gedenk, neyn, neyn, s'iz shoyn nisht geven keyn zeydes. ikh veys nisht, ikh hob nisht gezen keyner iz nisht gekumen.

00:09:34.961 --> 00:09:40.079
me iz geblibn dort, m'iz tsamgefaln iz men shoyn geven a fartiker.

00:09:42.448 --> 00:09:48.787
yetst ir aleyn, oder ayere brider, shvester, hobn gehert tsu epes tsienistishe organizatsyes far di milkhome.

00:09:47.488 --> 00:09:49.467
tsu di mizrakhi.

00:09:49.762 --> 00:09:52.719
yo mir, s'iz geven a YIKHUD,

00:09:52.882 --> 00:09:55.565
un ahin flegn mir geyn shabes,

00:09:55.646 --> 00:10:03.267
un me, dort flegn mir lernen, un zogn, un shraybn, shabes hot men nisht geshribn, ober me fleg a mol oykh gebn a heym,

00:10:03.882 --> 00:10:06.501
 s'iz geven zeyer yidishlekh.

00:10:07.068 --> 00:10:10.775
ir hot gevust shoyn in yene tsaytn hot ir gehert vegn Erets-Yisroel?

00:10:10.379 --> 00:10:14.165
yo. yo, me fleg redn derfun.

00:10:11.102 --> 00:10:12.767
ir hot ge-, me fleg aykh dertseyln?

00:10:14.231 --> 00:10:17.679
ober ver hot den gekent kumen? me hot den gelozt?

00:10:17.767 --> 00:10:21.732
un nokh a zakh, s'iz geven rabonim, men iz zikh gegangen rotn.

00:10:21.732 --> 00:10:24.035
hobn zey gezogt, "me broykh nisht forn ahin."

00:10:25.361 --> 00:10:27.937
ir gedenkt epes nemen fun rabonim?

00:10:29.900 --> 00:10:32.088
tsufelik, efsher gedenkt ir emetsn?

00:10:31.761 --> 00:10:38.500
s'iz geven der dem kretshnever rebe, vos er iz do ot ot, der zeyde

00:10:38.619 --> 00:10:43.214
oykh gezogt,

00:10:43.214 --> 00:10:45.381
Mendlboym? Birnboym?

00:10:45.206 --> 00:10:46.263
Teytlboym?

00:10:45.908 --> 00:10:49.956
Teytlboym, epes azoy. Teytlboym iz geven der sigeter rov!

00:10:52.589 --> 00:11:01.125
un s'iz geven rebes mit rebes, un me, s'iz geven velkhe zey hobn gezogt nisht forn.

00:11:02.840 --> 00:11:05.180
Siget iz dokh geven a groyse shtot.

00:11:04.410 --> 00:11:06.107
a groyse shtot.

00:11:06.047 --> 00:11:09.703
s'iz dort, akhuts di yidn hobn dort gevoynt oykh kristn, nisht keyn yidn.

00:11:09.355 --> 00:11:10.803
nisht keyn yidn.

00:11:10.113 --> 00:11:16.435
vos far a batsiungen iz geven tsvishn di yidn un nisht di yidn in di, far di rumeynishe tsayt?

00:11:16.404 --> 00:11:18.607
zeyer gut gelebt.

00:11:18.607 --> 00:11:23.107
say, mit di rumenishe goyim un say mit di ungarishe.

00:11:23.107 --> 00:11:27.107
in hoyf vu mir ho'mir gevoynt, ho'mir gehat shkheynim,

00:11:27.107 --> 00:11:31.803
ungarishe, me hot shtark gehaltn fun der mame Hober NENI, Hober...

00:11:31.821 --> 00:11:38.517
s'iz geven, un az ikh bin aroysgekumen, bald hot men ongehoybn redn ungarish. in shtub nor yidish.

00:11:38.919 --> 00:11:40.398
in shtub hot men geredt yidish.

00:11:39.928 --> 00:11:46.732
yo, me hot gebentsht. un s'iz geven shabes, un yedn tog, zeyer balebatish.

00:11:47.392 --> 00:11:50.767
me hot nisht gehat mit di goyim gornisht.

00:11:50.630 --> 00:11:54.050
ober zey zenen geven laytish, zey hobn zikh nisht getshepet far di rumeynishe tsayt.

00:11:52.625 --> 00:11:56.339
NO, NO, NO, NO, keyner gornisht.

00:11:58.275 --> 00:12:05.002
yetst dos lebn tsit zikh azoy bay aykh, azoy vi ir zogt, nisht keyn laykht lebn, ober men hot gelebt balebatish zogt ir.

00:12:04.607 --> 00:12:05.785
yo.

00:12:06.020 --> 00:12:07.637
biz ven,

00:12:07.637 --> 00:12:09.761
ven zenen arayngegangen di ungarn tsu aykh?

00:12:09.696 --> 00:12:12.232
in fir un fertsik.

00:12:12.250 --> 00:12:15.142
dos, in in fertsik.

00:12:14.846 --> 00:12:15.870
in fertsik.

00:12:15.943 --> 00:12:18.485
az di ungarn zenen arayngegangen in fertsik...

00:12:18.107 --> 00:12:19.500
hot men shoyn gefilt.

00:12:19.335 --> 00:12:22.046
vos hot ir gefilt? far a untershid?

00:12:22.071 --> 00:12:28.500
vos, zey hobn shoyn, zey hobn geshtelt in ale zaytn, nokhgekukt nokh di mentshn, nokhgeshmekt un un un,

00:12:28.535 --> 00:12:32.553
un s'iz shoyn nisht geven, me hot shoyn ayngetsoygn dos esnvarg,

00:12:32.553 --> 00:12:36.285
mit a ye-, hot men gefilt shtark. shtark.

00:12:36.176 --> 00:12:39.680
me hot getshepet ayere brider far yene tsaytn?

00:12:40.007 --> 00:12:41.014
fun onheyb?

00:12:40.928 --> 00:12:44.732
dem groysn nisht, dem kleynem yo.

00:12:44.732 --> 00:12:46.946
er iz avek keyn Budapest.

00:12:46.946 --> 00:12:48.500
er hot gearbet.

00:12:48.500 --> 00:12:53.500
un, privat, er fleg makhn di goldene dos.

00:12:53.500 --> 00:12:56.535
zeyer, er hot shtark sheyn fardint.

00:12:56.625 --> 00:13:01.535
un er er hot undz gehaltn, shoyn demolts ze'mir undz shoyn geven negidim.

00:13:01.607 --> 00:13:07.071
hot men gefregt in hoyf, "fun vu nemt ir Hober NENI? ir leygt aroyf klafter holts in hoyf!"

00:13:07.892 --> 00:13:09.839
"der fun oybn git mir."

00:13:12.018 --> 00:13:16.029
iz der bruder geven in Budapest, un er fleg aykh shikn...

00:13:15.839 --> 00:13:21.232
yo. yo, yo. oyf peysekh iz er aheymgekumen, in tsvey un fertsik,

00:13:21.410 --> 00:13:23.321
iz er aheymgekumen

00:13:23.339 --> 00:13:29.410
tsum seyder, er hot gebrengt fun dort, s'iz nisht geven, ober in shvartsn iz geven aldings,

00:13:29.428 --> 00:13:34.071
er iz gekumen ongepakt un gebrengt far der mame, "dayge dikh nisht,

00:13:34.071 --> 00:13:35.517
ales vet zayn."

00:13:35.517 --> 00:13:38.339
un nokhn seyder, nokh alemen

00:13:38.339 --> 00:13:41.089
hot men zikh avekgezetst un geredt,

00:13:42.053 --> 00:13:45.750
"mame, zog mir, vos vos voltstu gevolt?

00:13:45.857 --> 00:13:49.250
velkhe shtub?" vayl undz ho'mir gevoynt in dire gelt.

00:13:49.910 --> 00:13:53.591
ho'mir im ongekukt, vi azoy ken a kind azoy? er hot

00:13:53.591 --> 00:13:57.089
shtark a sakh, un er iz geven zeyer a shparzam,

00:13:57.089 --> 00:14:00.625
er iz nisht geven keyn, er zol varfn mitn gelt.

00:14:00.642 --> 00:14:03.678
in in tsvey un fertsik.

00:14:03.857 --> 00:14:06.071
er iz tsurikgegan fun peysekh,

00:14:06.071 --> 00:14:07.982
hot men im bald ayngerufn.

00:14:08.857 --> 00:14:12.142
iz mayn shvester aropgeforn keyn Budapest,

00:14:12.142 --> 00:14:16.125
un hot aheymgebrengt dos gelt. un hot nokh aheymgebrengt dos gold.

00:14:16.375 --> 00:14:21.464
un er hot zikh ayngekoyft nebekh, un er hot gebroykht avekgeyn in MUNKOSAZE.

00:14:21.464 --> 00:14:24.892
un in dray un fertsik iz gekumen an UNK.

00:14:25.497 --> 00:14:26.747
neh.

00:14:25.560 --> 00:14:26.753
iz gekumen vos?

00:14:26.747 --> 00:14:28.428
a az er iz ahingekumen.

00:14:29.017 --> 00:14:30.160
yoy.

00:14:29.053 --> 00:14:31.629
vu? oyf velkhn plats, veyst ir nisht?

00:14:32.375 --> 00:14:34.071
ikh ken nisht zogn.

00:14:34.464 --> 00:14:36.767
er iz dokh geven in MUNKOSAZOT.

00:14:36.767 --> 00:14:39.660
ikh veys vu, vey iz tsum got nebekh vu er ligt.

00:14:39.363 --> 00:14:41.568
dos iz bay dem ungarishn militer.

00:14:41.321 --> 00:14:43.387
yo, yo, yo, dort iz er geblibn.

00:14:42.840 --> 00:14:43.965
alts yid.

00:14:43.853 --> 00:14:48.514
als yid, zikher mit di gele band. undz ho'mir getrogn di shterns.

00:14:50.982 --> 00:14:51.875
zikher.

00:14:51.513 --> 00:14:56.418
iz hot geven a, hot ir gehat a zeyer a shlekhte bsure in dray un fertsikstn yor.

00:14:55.642 --> 00:15:03.642
di mame nebekh hot geveynt, az me hot zi nisht gekent an- az me hert aza bsure. fun aza goldn kind. vi azoy...

00:15:03.785 --> 00:15:06.625
ober ales iz geven fun dem fun oybn.

00:15:06.718 --> 00:15:09.311
er iz geven a getrayer zun un a getrayer bruder.

00:15:09.053 --> 00:15:15.071
shtark getray. shtark getray. ir kont zen nokh der bild. zayn, zayn,

00:15:16.125 --> 00:15:17.536
ikh ken mikh nisht dermanen,

00:15:17.536 --> 00:15:20.089
ikh leyg avek ikh zol nisht zen tsu shtark.

00:15:20.125 --> 00:15:23.357
vayl se tut mikh zeyer vey dos harts. ikh gedenk im zeyer.

00:15:23.238 --> 00:15:28.194
zent ir geblibn lebn dort unter di ungarn vayter biz...

00:15:27.178 --> 00:15:29.089
biz fir un fertsik.

00:15:29.145 --> 00:15:32.835
un dort iz geven in der heym, zent ir geven, di shvesters,

00:15:32.357 --> 00:15:38.410
di shvester, mayn bruder hot khasene gehat, der Leyzer. un er hot shoyn gehat tsvey kinder.

00:15:35.658 --> 00:15:36.682
Leyzer.

00:15:38.410 --> 00:15:52.053
er hot gevoynt dos tsveyte hoyf fun undz. azoy me hot zikh gezen mistome, me hot gegan un gekumen, un far a noyt a mol hot er a shtup geton epes, far der mame, ober se hot ir nisht tsu shtark oysgefelt,

00:15:52.053 --> 00:15:54.250
vayl er hot ibergelozt zeyer a sakh.

00:15:54.626 --> 00:15:59.970
iz vos zhe iz geshen, dertseylt mir ven in fir fertsikstn, un vos hot, vos hot pasirt in fir un fertsikstn?

00:16:00.214 --> 00:16:01.892
nu, in fir un fertsik,

00:16:01.928 --> 00:16:05.696
s'iz gekumen in in merts,

00:16:05.790 --> 00:16:07.606
in merts, in april.

00:16:06.725 --> 00:16:08.323
s'iz geven nokh peysekh?

00:16:08.375 --> 00:16:09.053
nokh peysekh,

00:16:08.733 --> 00:16:10.094
april ober.

00:16:09.548 --> 00:16:11.807
arayngekumen di daytshn,

00:16:13.535 --> 00:16:17.571
un zey hobn zikh bazetst bayn undz in hoyf oykh. fornt.

00:16:17.660 --> 00:16:21.357
tsu der gas. undz ho'mir gevoynt der tsveyter tir.

00:16:21.464 --> 00:16:24.339
geven genug pakhedik,

00:16:24.535 --> 00:16:30.321
zey hobn ober geredt, un zey hobn gegrist un me hot zikh nebekh gehaltn azoy.

00:16:30.678 --> 00:16:34.285
un nokh dem hot men gemakht a geto.

00:16:34.660 --> 00:16:36.928
un, dos eynikl iz gekumen...

00:16:35.970 --> 00:16:37.956
ven hot men gemakht di geto?

00:16:37.892 --> 00:16:39.750
in in april.

00:16:39.530 --> 00:16:41.229
april fir un fertsik?

00:16:40.607 --> 00:16:41.732
yo.

00:16:42.053 --> 00:16:44.107
ikh meyn nokh peysekh shoyn.

00:16:44.571 --> 00:16:50.785
bald nokh peysekh, s'iz geven tsvey tsi dray vokh in geto, taken in der gas, vu me ho'mir gevoynt.

00:16:50.785 --> 00:16:52.285
nor aroptsir.

00:16:52.589 --> 00:16:54.053
bayn a mume.

00:16:54.607 --> 00:16:56.267
bay der mame's a...

00:16:56.338 --> 00:16:58.678
vi lang zent ir geven in geto?

00:16:58.392 --> 00:16:59.839
a dray vokhn.

00:16:59.679 --> 00:17:01.428
mit vemen tsuzamen?

00:17:01.089 --> 00:17:03.714
mit der mame, mit mayn shvester,

00:17:03.750 --> 00:17:04.910
un ZE HU.

00:17:04.522 --> 00:17:06.541
in der bruder mit zayn familye?

00:17:06.267 --> 00:17:09.000
yener hot gevoynt oyf an ander plats.

00:17:09.382 --> 00:17:10.828
un oykh in Siget?

00:17:10.250 --> 00:17:11.410
oykh in Siget.

00:17:11.070 --> 00:17:13.241
im hot men nisht arayngefirt in geto?

00:17:13.107 --> 00:17:14.517
er, an andern geto.

00:17:14.478 --> 00:17:16.194
oh, dort geven nokh a geto.

00:17:14.521 --> 00:17:16.120
s'iz geven tsvey

00:17:16.122 --> 00:17:17.595
s'iz geven tsvey getos.

00:17:17.364 --> 00:17:19.518
oh, in Siget zenen geven tsvey getos.

00:17:18.553 --> 00:17:19.910
yo.

00:17:19.946 --> 00:17:22.657
hot ir gehat farbindungen mitn bruder?

00:17:22.071 --> 00:17:24.107
 me, ikh hob mikh aroysgekhapt.

00:17:24.160 --> 00:17:26.357
ikh hob nisht getsaygt far a yidishe.

00:17:27.017 --> 00:17:29.250
un ikh hob avekgenumen dem shtern,

00:17:29.375 --> 00:17:35.982
ikh hob dokh getrogn a shtern, un ikh fleg geyn, ikh fleg mikh a khap ton tsu di kinderlekh, ikh hob gebenkt, un...

00:17:36.053 --> 00:17:38.767
me hot getun, me hot zikh ayngeshtelt.

00:17:38.745 --> 00:17:41.777
yetst dray vokhn zent ir geven, zogt ir, in geto.

00:17:40.732 --> 00:17:42.160
yo.

00:17:42.204 --> 00:17:45.776
ir kent zikh dermanen, in vos far a badingungen zent ir geven in geto?

00:17:45.875 --> 00:17:47.375
in in geto.

00:17:47.410 --> 00:17:52.517
vos me hot gehat, fun fun, me hot zikh ibergetrogn fun di shtub,

00:17:52.553 --> 00:17:55.196
un me iz gegan ahin, azoy hot men gelebt.

00:17:56.571 --> 00:17:59.267
a por zakhn hot men getrogn,

00:17:59.267 --> 00:18:04.517
un di, s'iz geblibn genug in shtub, un me hot getrogn dort iz es oykh geblibn,

00:18:04.517 --> 00:18:08.125
vayl se hobn gevoynt etlekhe familyes in eyn dire.

00:18:08.250 --> 00:18:11.357
m'iz gekumen fun fun,

00:18:11.357 --> 00:18:17.250
Siget iz geven groys, un di mishpokhes zenen gevezn fun, fun di mumes tsad,

00:18:17.250 --> 00:18:18.142
groys,

00:18:18.285 --> 00:18:21.875
men hot zikh derzen afile in shtal, tsvishn di ki, hot men oykh geshlofn.

00:18:23.196 --> 00:18:24.696
un ven ze'mir,

00:18:25.428 --> 00:18:28.750
di ungern zenen dort shoyn gevezn, hobn zey undz

00:18:28.750 --> 00:18:33.464
aroysgevorfn, aroys fun der shtub, gedriget un men gepushket,

00:18:32.289 --> 00:18:33.465
fun ayer shtub.

00:18:33.714 --> 00:18:36.642
fun fun der, funem geto.

00:18:35.630 --> 00:18:38.538
oh, far dem, ir, ikh hob nokh gevolt visn far dem.

00:18:38.550 --> 00:18:42.679
ven men hot oykh aroysgenumen fun ayer shtub, hot ir ibergelozt ale zakhn in der heym?

00:18:42.035 --> 00:18:45.142
ale zakhn, ales iz geblibn...

00:18:43.815 --> 00:18:48.939
s'iz geven faln vos ir hot epes ibergegebn tsu goyim zey zoln, hashgokhe UNK?

00:18:47.321 --> 00:18:50.642
dort bay der shtub nisht.

00:18:50.678 --> 00:18:55.714
vayl s'iz geven a moser, hot gevoynt di andere tir, eyner KOVATSH PETER.

00:18:55.767 --> 00:18:58.785
a biterer, an ek.

00:18:58.785 --> 00:18:59.857
ober,

00:18:59.875 --> 00:19:01.720
ikh hob mikh gemakht nisht visndik.

00:19:01.740 --> 00:19:08.375
ven me hot undz gefirt shoyn funem geto tsum RAKEVET tsu tsu forn, avektsuforn

00:19:08.375 --> 00:19:12.732
iz er geshtanen in shtot bayn, bayn a bekeray,

00:19:12.732 --> 00:19:14.839
un er hot ongehoybn shrayen,

00:19:15.071 --> 00:19:17.982
 oyf ungarish. meg ikh zogn?

00:19:16.940 --> 00:19:17.778
yo.

00:19:18.375 --> 00:19:22.678
"NI NI MOSH VISIK O SOMSEDASE!"

00:19:21.547 --> 00:19:22.807
vos heyst dos?

00:19:22.732 --> 00:19:25.964
"hitstert firt men mayne shkheynim, kuk zey, dort geyen zey!"

00:19:25.749 --> 00:19:26.975
er hot zikh gefreyt.

00:19:25.964 --> 00:19:26.886
undz ze-

00:19:26.946 --> 00:19:32.500
er hot geredt tsum andern, un un undz ze'mir gegan, ikh hob gezen vi er redt, vos er tut.

00:19:32.732 --> 00:19:35.036
a biterer ant-

00:19:34.743 --> 00:19:35.817
antisemit.

00:19:35.362 --> 00:19:38.362
antisemit, an araynzoger eyner.

00:19:38.732 --> 00:19:39.678
a goy.

00:19:40.633 --> 00:19:42.804
hot ir gornisht ibergelozt bay di goyim?

00:19:42.571 --> 00:19:45.982
dort nisht, ober in geto,

00:19:46.267 --> 00:19:48.892
vu di mume hot gevoynt, nu,

00:19:49.125 --> 00:19:53.892
undz hot zi antfangen in shtub, vayl ze'mir geven zeyer noent,

00:19:54.023 --> 00:19:57.071
hot zi yo gegebn. dort bay

00:19:57.071 --> 00:19:58.714
epes a tsvey shkheynim.

00:19:58.875 --> 00:20:01.607
ober s'iz nisht geven ver es zol zen

00:20:01.642 --> 00:20:03.732
vi vos zi git.

00:20:04.000 --> 00:20:06.964
vayl eyn zun iz avek mit undz,

00:20:08.053 --> 00:20:11.232
koydem iz er geven in in MUNKOSAZOT.

00:20:11.303 --> 00:20:16.875
un er iz aheymgekumen in dem tog ven me hot im gebroykht, ven mir ho'mir gebroykht avekgeyn.

00:20:18.035 --> 00:20:22.267
un der anderer iz geven ayngeshpart in KISTARCA.

00:20:23.375 --> 00:20:28.660
vayl der KOVATSH hot im ayngemasert, az er iz a komunist.

00:20:28.767 --> 00:20:31.000
me hot im nebekh azoy fil geshlogn,

00:20:31.053 --> 00:20:33.160
az er iz haynt azoy. er lebt.

00:20:33.178 --> 00:20:35.946
azoy iz er. er iz in Amerike.

00:20:36.071 --> 00:20:37.178
dos iz es.

00:20:37.303 --> 00:20:39.625
s'iz geven zeyer biter shver.

00:20:39.875 --> 00:20:41.732
un un der ho- iz

00:20:42.214 --> 00:20:48.589
kleyner bruder iz aheymgekumen gikher. s'iz bafrayt gevorn, ikh bin gekumen shpet aheym.

00:20:48.696 --> 00:20:52.071
der bruder vos er iz gegan mit mir oyf a mol,

00:20:52.089 --> 00:20:55.982
der der hot nisht gevust, vi vos me hot ibergelozt.

00:20:56.732 --> 00:21:00.178
der iz aroysgegangen shoyn, er geven in der heym,

00:21:00.321 --> 00:21:06.370
un er iz arayn dort tsun eyn shokhn, tsum andern, azoy zikh bakont. un a klal, me hot ongehoybn

00:21:06.370 --> 00:21:08.214
me hot aroysgenumen zakhn.

00:21:08.232 --> 00:21:11.392
un me hot ongehoybn tsurikgebn. veynik.

00:21:10.307 --> 00:21:12.394
dos redt ir shoyn nokhn bafrayen.

00:21:12.857 --> 00:21:14.982
deys iz fun nokhn bafrayen.

00:21:13.985 --> 00:21:17.180
fun, lomir, vegn dem vel mir nokh redn, dos vet men nokh redn.

00:21:16.024 --> 00:21:17.453
OKAY. OKAY.

00:21:17.225 --> 00:21:19.087
ikh halt, mir haltn yetst

00:21:19.098 --> 00:21:23.584
ven men firt aykh aroys, vu, vos hot ir ge-, farn dem, zeyendik in geto,

00:21:23.621 --> 00:21:27.834
hot ir gevust az me geyt aykh ergets firn? me hot geredt epes vegn dem far dem?

00:21:26.464 --> 00:21:30.160
me hot nisht gekent mitnemen gornisht.

00:21:30.160 --> 00:21:33.107
me hot a makh geton a finef a reye,

00:21:33.160 --> 00:21:37.553
nu, a shtikl broyt epes, un bald hobn di tshenderes

00:21:37.589 --> 00:21:38.892
aroysgedriget.

00:21:39.500 --> 00:21:42.000
un s'iz geblibn di ofene tir

00:21:42.000 --> 00:21:46.464
mit alem gutn in shtub, vayl yeder hot tsamgebrengt es zol zayn,

00:21:46.517 --> 00:21:52.071
un di goyim, vos zey hobn gevoynt dortn, ot di zenen, undz ze'mir nokh geven oyf der gas,

00:21:52.071 --> 00:21:53.910
zenen zey shoyn gelofn

00:21:53.946 --> 00:21:56.267
shlepn avektrogn.

00:21:56.500 --> 00:22:01.571
dos iz geven. un keyn Daytshland ho'mir undz nisht getrogn gornisht.

00:22:02.130 --> 00:22:06.143
ver hot aykh gefirt fun geto tsu dem,

00:22:06.146 --> 00:22:07.490
tsu dem RAKEVET?

00:22:08.089 --> 00:22:10.732
di ungerishe s- soldatn.

00:22:10.787 --> 00:22:13.113
eng- nisht keyn englishe, ir ir

00:22:12.031 --> 00:22:13.303
ungerishe.

00:22:13.149 --> 00:22:16.063
ungerishe, ah, ungerishe soldatn, yo.

00:22:15.214 --> 00:22:19.357
ungerishe soldatn hobn undz gefirt tsum RAKEVET.

00:22:19.357 --> 00:22:20.678
finef a reye.

00:22:20.732 --> 00:22:23.089
un mir ho'mir gehat an alte mume

00:22:23.357 --> 00:22:27.607
vos zi iz gezesn bay mayn mame, vayl zi hot nebekh nisht gehat vu tsu zayn,

00:22:28.767 --> 00:22:32.214
un ikh hob zi gefirt in DRESARE,

00:22:32.267 --> 00:22:35.982
ongekumen tsum RAKEVET, biter shver.

00:22:36.232 --> 00:22:37.553
ober mit gornisht.

00:22:37.553 --> 00:22:40.321
gehat a b- a shireml in di hant.

00:22:40.321 --> 00:22:42.214
arayngevorfn in naye hoyf.

00:22:42.357 --> 00:22:45.928
zi hot nebekh gehat, di takhrikhim hot zi zikh mitgenumen.

00:22:45.964 --> 00:22:48.785
in keyshele, arayngevorfn an andere.

00:22:48.857 --> 00:22:52.946
s'iz geven tsores, ober koydem hot men undz arayngefirt in a shul,

00:22:53.410 --> 00:22:55.553
in di Makhzikey-Toyre shul,

00:22:55.553 --> 00:22:57.703
un dort ho'mir ibergenekhtikt.

00:22:57.785 --> 00:23:01.214
un in der fri hot men a zog geton, "finef a reye!"

00:23:01.375 --> 00:23:03.821
un UNK, men iz gegangen vayter.

00:23:03.656 --> 00:23:06.806
v- vi lay-, vi vayt hot ir gedarft geyn fun dortn?

00:23:05.214 --> 00:23:07.928
yoy, a sakh.

00:23:08.017 --> 00:23:10.678
di, deys iz geven

00:23:10.678 --> 00:23:13.982
vayt, un in der RAKEVET...

00:23:12.161 --> 00:23:13.894
tsum tsug iz geven vayt?

00:23:13.982 --> 00:23:18.571
yo, shtark a sakh. un UNK, ikh hob nebekh geshlept, eyner hot zikh geshlept dem andern.

00:23:18.371 --> 00:23:21.352
iz vu lang zent ir gegangen, a tog, mer vi a tog?

00:23:20.750 --> 00:23:24.275
NO, NO, efsher a sho, anderthalb.

00:23:24.058 --> 00:23:25.166
etlekhe sho.

00:23:25.061 --> 00:23:25.649
yo.

00:23:25.847 --> 00:23:29.824
ir zent ongekumen tsu dem tsug, vos iz, vos iz geshen dortn?

00:23:29.339 --> 00:23:32.839
nu, dort hot men, hobn zikh geshtelt di vagonen.

00:23:32.928 --> 00:23:34.803
un me hot undz aynvagonirt.

00:23:35.263 --> 00:23:37.907
vi arum hot men aykh aynvagonirt, kent ir dertseyln?

00:23:37.946 --> 00:23:40.642
vi, vos heyst vi azoy? me hot genumen

00:23:40.642 --> 00:23:44.000
 vifl ze'mir geven? epes a zibetsik.

00:23:44.232 --> 00:23:46.071
vifl s'iz arayn.

00:23:46.875 --> 00:23:50.607
az s'iz gevezn, dem rebe, vos er voynt do ot ot,

00:23:50.607 --> 00:23:52.267
zayn zeyde,

00:23:52.339 --> 00:23:53.500
mitn vayb,

00:23:53.500 --> 00:23:55.928
undz ho'mir. zey zenen geven mit undz in geto,

00:23:56.410 --> 00:24:00.928
hot men shoyn, zi geven bayn undz in RAKEVE-, in vagon,

00:24:00.928 --> 00:24:04.857
un im hot men shoyn opgeshpart. un er iz geven in andern.

00:24:04.875 --> 00:24:08.750
un di koyles vos dey hobn gezogt tilim, un gedavnt un geshrign.

00:24:09.285 --> 00:24:11.714
ze'mir ongekumen fraytik far nakhts,

00:24:12.035 --> 00:24:15.946
hot genumen di rebetsn hot gegebn likht, me zol hobn ontsutsindn.

00:24:15.964 --> 00:24:17.375
ver hot den gebroykht?

00:24:17.500 --> 00:24:20.017
punkt demolt ze'mir ongekumen keyn Daytshland.

00:24:20.100 --> 00:24:21.596
vu zent ir ongekumen?

00:24:21.821 --> 00:24:23.214
keyn Oyshvits.

00:24:23.154 --> 00:24:24.110
Oyshvits.

00:24:24.076 --> 00:24:25.000
yo.

00:24:25.398 --> 00:24:26.590
ir kent,

00:24:26.934 --> 00:24:31.063
dos for-, vi lang zent ir geforn mitn tsug biz ir zent ongekumen keyn Oyshvits?

00:24:31.339 --> 00:24:33.982
ikh veys? m'iz geforn.

00:24:33.982 --> 00:24:36.107
men iz geforn genug.

00:24:35.237 --> 00:24:36.733
vifl, etlekhe teg?

00:24:36.410 --> 00:24:39.428
 tsvey tog efsher, ikh vey-, ikh ken nisht zogn.

00:24:39.101 --> 00:24:42.133
di badingungen in di vagon zenen geven...?

00:24:41.803 --> 00:24:45.500
gornisht hot men nisht gegebn, nor deys vos me hot gehat epes.

00:24:45.589 --> 00:24:50.089
m- m'iz taken, s'iz nishto vos tsu zogn.

00:24:50.142 --> 00:24:51.785
me ken es nisht gleybn.

00:24:51.785 --> 00:24:54.892
me flegt pishn un gebn zi kinder tsu trinken.

00:24:55.183 --> 00:24:56.932
afile keyn vaser iz nisht geven.

00:24:59.303 --> 00:25:04.803
na. ze'mir geven azoy a- tsamgeshturket, ale HET, az s'iz geven a pakhed.

00:25:05.342 --> 00:25:07.496
ir kent mir dertseyln

00:25:07.670 --> 00:25:10.584
vos ir gedenkt fun onkumen keyn Oyshvits?

00:25:11.410 --> 00:25:13.535
onkumen keyn Oyshvits?

00:25:13.535 --> 00:25:16.196
m'iz ongekumen fraytik far nakhts,

00:25:16.196 --> 00:25:20.250
iz zikh a shtark geton da- daytshe TSAVA,

00:25:21.142 --> 00:25:28.857
me hot geefnt di di di tirn, un me hot gezogt aroys, un vos me hot zol men dort lozn.

00:25:30.321 --> 00:25:34.821
keyn groyse zakhn hot keyner nisht gehat epes stam.

00:25:35.089 --> 00:25:40.785
un me hot shtoyn a makh geton, eynem aher, un eynem, aher un me hot nisht gevust.

00:25:39.716 --> 00:25:42.562
vos heyst aher un aher, vos, oyf links un oyf rekhts?

00:25:42.660 --> 00:25:48.839
yo. yo. me hot gemakht tsu finef a reye, un me hot undz shoyn tseteylt, in der minut fun der,

00:25:48.875 --> 00:25:50.178
fun der mame,

00:25:50.642 --> 00:25:52.071
un fun der mume,

00:25:52.660 --> 00:25:54.750
teykef, undz ze'mir shoyn nisht geven,

00:25:54.750 --> 00:25:58.107
ikh bin avek mit mayn shvester, nisht mer.

00:25:58.920 --> 00:26:02.948
un fun, fun vemen hot men aykh tsesheydt, fun der mame un fun der mume.

00:26:01.964 --> 00:26:04.000
fun der mame, fun der mume,

00:26:03.881 --> 00:26:05.732
der bruder hot nisht ge⟨UNK⟩.

00:26:05.375 --> 00:26:08.285
nisht mit undz, er iz avek in andern geto.

00:26:09.428 --> 00:26:12.928
un eyner iz geblibn in MUNKOSAZOT. un fartik.

00:26:12.928 --> 00:26:15.464
se hot zikh oysgelozt, ze'mir geblibn azoy.

00:26:16.233 --> 00:26:21.138
vos zhe gedenkt, dertseylt vos ir gedenkt vayter, vos iz geshen mit aykh in Oyshvits.

00:26:20.887 --> 00:26:21.857
nu, in Oyshvits

00:26:22.375 --> 00:26:26.696
hot men genumen, undz ho'mir den gevust vu me firt di alte?

00:26:26.839 --> 00:26:29.250
tsi vu me firt froyen mit kinder?

00:26:29.285 --> 00:26:34.000
un az ver es hot gevolt helfn far emetser vos zi hot gehat tsu tsvey kinder,

00:26:34.053 --> 00:26:36.196
iz zi oykh gegangen in fayer arayn.

00:26:36.214 --> 00:26:37.767
hot gemegt zayn a yunge.

00:26:37.785 --> 00:26:40.589
zey hobn nisht gekukt, di fintstere daytshn, vos zey tuen.

00:26:41.035 --> 00:26:44.732
ober me hot nisht gevust. me hot undz gefirt in bod arayn.

00:26:47.232 --> 00:26:53.803
un ineveynik ven ze'mir ongekumen in dem zal, hot men gezogt oystun komplet naket.

00:26:54.482 --> 00:26:55.696
oygn glezer,

00:26:55.750 --> 00:26:56.964
aropleygn.

00:26:56.964 --> 00:27:02.446
a ringl, az me hot epes gehat, aropleygn. iz geven a kestl, me hot...

00:27:02.857 --> 00:27:04.821
un m'iz geblibn naket.

00:27:05.267 --> 00:27:08.071
un nokh dem hot men undz gefirt in a bod.

00:27:09.642 --> 00:27:10.750
mener

00:27:10.857 --> 00:27:13.107
zenen gekumen, hobn undz razirt.

00:27:13.107 --> 00:27:14.911
yoy, ikh zog aykh!

00:27:14.911 --> 00:27:16.393
deys, deys...

00:27:16.393 --> 00:27:20.315
undz ho'mir zikh ongekukt eyner dem andern, me hot zikh nisht derkent.

00:27:20.315 --> 00:27:23.582
me hot nisht gevust, ver bistu, tsi ver bistu.

00:27:23.582 --> 00:27:28.779
ver veyst, vos tut di mame? vu hot men zi gefirt? un vu hot men zi gefirt? un nokh a mol,

00:27:29.543 --> 00:27:31.419
un az got hot geholfn,

00:27:31.419 --> 00:27:36.525
a gantse nakht ze'mir undz geven in dey bod dort. gezesn, geshtanen,

00:27:36.549 --> 00:27:40.086
fun esn kumt nisht in frage, ver, vos?

00:27:40.086 --> 00:27:44.442
epes, dem eybershter's nisim, me hot durkhgefirt.

00:27:45.358 --> 00:27:49.680
un, ven ikh bin arayngekumen in BLOK arayn,

00:27:49.680 --> 00:27:54.412
iz geshtanen oyfgeshribn fun droysn, "der BLOK iz dayn heym."

00:27:54.412 --> 00:27:56.886
"der BLOK iz dayn heym."

00:27:56.886 --> 00:28:00.153
nu, vos veys'mir undz, plutsem aza zakh?

00:28:00.153 --> 00:28:02.921
me kumt arayn, iz geven poylishe

00:28:03.053 --> 00:28:07.017
BLOKELTESTE, a shlekhte klaftes, az...

00:28:06.292 --> 00:28:08.379
ir gedenkt ir nomen, efsher?

00:28:07.660 --> 00:28:12.839
epes a PERKO, TERKO, epes a, nu, ikh veys vi azoy?

00:28:13.777 --> 00:28:15.777
zeyer shlekhte.

00:28:15.777 --> 00:28:17.955
"ir zet dort dem roykh?"

00:28:17.955 --> 00:28:20.330
"dort brent men ayere mames."

00:28:20.330 --> 00:28:24.812
tsu hern aza vort, iz a groyse zakh.

00:28:25.901 --> 00:28:31.448
zayt azoy gut, mir veln do zikh opshteln ibertsutoyshn a kasete, un shpeter mir veln vayter geyn.

00:28:30.886 --> 00:28:32.009
BAKASHA.
